    "updated_at": "2016-07-10T10:55:21Z",
    "body": "The \"tabs\" feature is only meaningful when there is a toolbar above, however in Electron we don't have a way to set native toolbar, even if we added support for \"tabs\", users would only get it with empty titlebar, which is useless.\n\nSo I'm closing this as won't fix due to Electron's limitation for native UI.\n"
