    "updated_at": "2016-08-03T21:54:17Z",
    "body": "Pretty much describing how all Browsers (Chrome) tab support works, which is not what Electron is about replicating.\n\nhttp://www.macworld.com/article/3088342/macs/how-to-use-tabs-in-macos-sierra.html\n\nThe ability to drag/move content (webview for example) between/from/to existing or new  renderer processes/BrowserWindow would enable a lot of similar scenarios in a cross-platform way as you can wrap your own HTML tab management around it, and there are plenty of good Tab libraries.\n"
  },
