    "created_at": "2016-09-23T20:06:41Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-09-23T20:06:41Z",
    "body": "We'd like to use native tabs in our application. It already works quite nice actually (see screenshot), if you set the dock setting to always use tabs. It even works with titlebar hidden (not hidden-inset). \n\n![schermafbeelding 2016-09-23 om 21 48 05](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/3015449/18799598/b5fc180c-81d8-11e6-986d-3ba82f07fed0.png)\n\nIt would be nice to force the usage of tabs, so the user doesn't have to change its dock preference.\n\nAlso the menu items @steverandy mentioned were not present in my app, but they are in the Api Demo's app though. \n"
  },
