    "created_at": "2016-09-24T14:18:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-09-24T14:18:17Z",
    "body": "@baconface it's about the behavior of the tabs; re-order animations (with preview window), drag and release tab to open in separate window, possibility to show tabs only in fullscreen mode (in stead of separate windows), menu items and shortcuts for navigating between tabs.\n\nMost of this would be possible with web technologies of course, but may take some more time to implement for devs.\n\nWith this we can assure that Electron application behave the same as other applications (as the user would expect). \n"
